14/*! \file */
15
16#include <config.h>
17
18#include <stdbool.h>
19
20#include <isc/mem.h>
21#include <isc/util.h>
22
23#include <dns/acl.h>
24
25#include <ns/listenlist.h>
26
27static void
28destroy(ns_listenlist_t *list);
29
30isc_result_t
31ns_listenelt_create(isc_mem_t *mctx, in_port_t port, isc_dscp_t dscp,
32 dns_acl_t *acl, ns_listenelt_t **target)
33{
34 ns_listenelt_t *elt = NULL;
35 REQUIRE(target != NULL && *target == NULL);
36 elt = isc_mem_get(mctx, sizeof(*elt));
37 if (elt == NULL)
38 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
39 elt->mctx = mctx;
40 ISC_LINK_INIT(elt, link);
41 elt->port = port;
42 elt->dscp = dscp;
43 elt->acl = acl;
44 *target = elt;
45 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
46}
47
48void
49ns_listenelt_destroy(ns_listenelt_t *elt) {
50 if (elt->acl != NULL)
51 dns_acl_detach(&elt->acl);
52 isc_mem_put(elt->mctx, elt, sizeof(*elt));
53}
54
55isc_result_t
56ns_listenlist_create(isc_mem_t *mctx, ns_listenlist_t **target) {
57 ns_listenlist_t *list = NULL;
58 REQUIRE(target != NULL && *target == NULL);
59 list = isc_mem_get(mctx, sizeof(*list));
60 if (list == NULL)
61 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
62 list->mctx = mctx;
63 list->refcount = 1;
64 ISC_LIST_INIT(list->elts);
65 *target = list;
66 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
67}
68
69static void
70destroy(ns_listenlist_t *list) {
71 ns_listenelt_t *elt, *next;
72 for (elt = ISC_LIST_HEAD(list->elts);
73 elt != NULL;
74 elt = next)
75 {
76 next = ISC_LIST_NEXT(elt, link);
77 ns_listenelt_destroy(elt);
78 }
79 isc_mem_put(list->mctx, list, sizeof(*list));
80}
81
82void
83ns_listenlist_attach(ns_listenlist_t *source, ns_listenlist_t **target) {
84 INSIST(source->refcount > 0);
85 source->refcount++;
86 *target = source;
87}
88
89void
90ns_listenlist_detach(ns_listenlist_t **listp) {
91 ns_listenlist_t *list = *listp;
92 INSIST(list->refcount > 0);
93 list->refcount--;
94 if (list->refcount == 0)
95 destroy(list);
96 *listp = NULL;
97}
98
99isc_result_t
100ns_listenlist_default(isc_mem_t *mctx, in_port_t port, isc_dscp_t dscp,
101 bool enabled, ns_listenlist_t **target)
102{
103 isc_result_t result;
104 dns_acl_t *acl = NULL;
105 ns_listenelt_t *elt = NULL;
106 ns_listenlist_t *list = NULL;
107
108 REQUIRE(target != NULL && *target == NULL);
109 if (enabled)
110 result = dns_acl_any(mctx, &acl);
111 else
112 result = dns_acl_none(mctx, &acl);
113 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
114 goto cleanup;
115
116 result = ns_listenelt_create(mctx, port, dscp, acl, &elt);
117 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
118 goto cleanup_acl;
119
120 result = ns_listenlist_create(mctx, &list);
121 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
122 goto cleanup_listenelt;
123
124 ISC_LIST_APPEND(list->elts, elt, link);
125
126 *target = list;
127 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
128
129 cleanup_listenelt:
130 ns_listenelt_destroy(elt);
131 cleanup_acl:
132 dns_acl_detach(&acl);
133 cleanup:
134 return (result);
135}
